[*] --> LevelInitialize

LevelInitialize --> Player_Turn : init_complete()

Player_Turn --> Mouse_Turn : end_player_turn()
Mouse_Turn --> Player_Turn : end_mouse_turn()

Player_Turn --> Pause : pause_pressed()
Mouse_Turn --> Pause : pause_pressed()
Pause --> Player_Turn : resume (from Player)
Pause --> Mouse_Turn : resume (from Mouse)

Player_Turn --> PowerMode : power_mode_pickup()
Mouse_Turn --> PowerMode : power_mode_pickup()
PowerMode --> Player_Turn : resumeTurn (if Player was active)
PowerMode --> Mouse_Turn : resumeTurn (if Mouse was active)

Player_Turn --> GameOver : mouse escaped / lose
Mouse_Turn --> GameOver : mouse escaped / lose

Player_Turn --> LevelComplete : mouse trapped / win
Mouse_Turn --> LevelComplete : mouse trapped / win

GameOver --> LevelInitialize : restartLevel()
LevelComplete --> LevelInitialize : nextLevel() / restartLevel()